    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras/1173925f33385a70b94464c1ec07db0d.avif?t=1741818820\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras_big/1173925f33385a70b94464c1ec07db0d.avif?t=1741818820 width=800 height=254 /></span><strong>Welcome to the Station</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A catastrophic explosion has left the station in ruins, its AI cores scattered and its secrets buried. Your mission? Extract the cores and uncover the truth—before the station shuts down for good.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras/d69fecd90da53d2d6f3055c1b833231b.avif?t=1741818820\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras_big/d69fecd90da53d2d6f3055c1b833231b.avif?t=1741818820 width=800 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tactical Top-Down Combat… Until Everything Changes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with an array of customizable weapons, you'll navigate the station, fend off infected machines, and adapt to its unpredictable dangers. But be warned—this is no ordinary mission. When the station goes offline, everything shifts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras/0a1418723e51b8a8e0e2757bc4f2e494.avif?t=1741818820\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras_big/0a1418723e51b8a8e0e2757bc4f2e494.avif?t=1741818820 width=800 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Surprising Twist: First-Person Survival Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suddenly, the rules change. The once-distant threats become up-close nightmares as you're thrown into intense <strong>first-person combat</strong>. Your reflexes, accuracy, and resourcefulness will be pushed to the limit. Can you survive when the station turns against you?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras/9f738eafac8795c8d5130886a9a77a03.avif?t=1741818820\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras_big/9f738eafac8795c8d5130886a9a77a03.avif?t=1741818820 width=800 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Retro Vibes with a Modern Edge</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixel Shader for a gritty, retro aesthetic</strong> – toggle it on or off anytime.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade &amp; Customize Your Arsenal</strong> – adapt your weapons to suit your playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Guided by Prize</strong> – your operator watches through security cameras, offering insight… and warnings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Station Full of Secrets</strong> – each AI core brings you closer to the truth, but some knowledge comes at a cost.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;You never know what might happen when you dig too deep.&quot;<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras/c5f8c17738eb9993dfd24fe0ab92eb9e.avif?t=1741818820\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295150/extras_big/c5f8c17738eb9993dfd24fe0ab92eb9e.avif?t=1741818820 width=800 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are You Ready?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the station. Adapt, survive, and prepare for the unexpected.</p>",
